# ASCII Art Test
# Tests multi-line ASCII art rendering with echo -e
Output examples/svgs/ascii-art.svg

Set Width 400
Set Theme github-dark
Set Template macos
Set Title "ASCII Art Demo"
Set FontSize 14

Type "echo -e ' ____  __     __ ____  \\n   |  _ \\\\ \\\\ \\\\   / /|  _ \\\\ \\n   | | | | \\\\ \\\\ / / | | | |\\n   | |_| |  \\\\ V /  | |_| |\\n   |____/    \\\\_/   |____/ '"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
